    3791,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86203110224?pwd=3XPsDxD6j7Dde4nHk4bPeJruRpCvww.1',
    '{"id":"01K99ZJ22YJJTRB4EYM1PP1JAY","title":"Powerhouse Gym // Marketers in Demand","summary":{"notes":"## **CRM and Lead Management Integration**\n\nThe team confirmed that **HubSpot** serves as the primary CRM with direct integration from **Meta ads** and website forms, streamlining lead capture and routing for sales follow-up (08:36).\n\n- Leads enter HubSpot either via Meta ads or website forms replaced with HubSpot forms, ensuring immediate capture and triggering drip campaigns (11:16).\n- The transition from HubSpot to **Data Track** is manual, requiring duplicate data entry and creating inefficiencies; this was highlighted as the biggest pain point by **Colin Costigan** and **Milan Wagner** (15:37).\n- The integration between HubSpot and Data Track relies on periodic polling via APIs every five minutes, incurring a monthly operational cost around **$300-$500** due to high volume usage (19:04).\n- HubSpot’s configuration, including custom objects and workflows, was tailored to fit the gym''s sales process, with **Colin** emphasizing that most time went into customizing workflows rather than building the integration itself (21:30).\n\n## **Sales and Communication Workflows**\n\nCurrent sales outreach is heavily manual, involving high-volume calling and texting supported by HubSpot and Air Call integrations, with room for automation improvement (31:17).\n\n- Sales reps make between **60 to 100 calls daily** each, totaling over **2,000 calls weekly**, and send up to **15,000 texts weekly**, all manually initiated via HubSpot-linked Air Call (32:05).\n- Lead outreach follows a cadence of **five to six contact attempts on day one**, combining calls, texts, and emails, with ongoing monthly follow-ups based on lead age and engagement (33:06).\n- Air Call manages inbound calls via a call queue system with fallback to a designated rep after missed calls, but lacks virtual receptionist or AI answering features currently (29:09).\n- The team is exploring HubSpot’s SMS marketing workflows to automate up to **25,000 messages per month**, which could reduce manual texting burden and improve lead engagement (35:50).\n\n## **Process Gaps and Limitations in Data Track**\n\nData Track lacks CRM capabilities and fails to support lead management, contract signing, and member engagement processes, necessitating additional platforms like HubSpot (46:09).\n\n- Data Track does not create lead accounts upon online waiver or phone signup, requiring reps to manually input member info and process payments, increasing administrative load (15:46).\n- Contract signing is manual or in-person only, with no electronic signature support, causing missed agreements and compliance risks as some liability forms are not captured timely (13:07).\n- Data Track’s reporting on member activity and churn is inconsistent and unreliable, complicating efforts to analyze retention, engagement, and sales effectiveness (58:22).\n- The personal training upsell and member engagement functions are rudimentary, relying on manual list pulls from Data Track and offline calling, with no current automation or campaign tracking (50:59).\n\n## **Analytics, Reporting, and Member Retention**\n\nThe group identified a pressing need for better visibility into sales performance, lead conversion, and member churn to drive smarter decision-making (53:47).\n\n- HubSpot can generate reports to track lead-to-member conversion rates by cohort, but this capability has not been fully leveraged by the team yet (55:46).\n- Sales leadership currently relies on manual tracking of individual rep performance through closing percentages and call volumes, but lacks integrated dashboards combining calls, texts, and sales results (54:34).\n- Understanding member churn drivers and personas is hindered by inconsistent Data Track data, limiting the ability to target retention efforts effectively (58:22).\n- The team expressed interest in cohort analysis and customer health scoring concepts from SaaS, aiming to segment members by behavior to predict and reduce churn, but lacks tools to implement this yet (01:00:55).\n\n## **Future Automation and AI Opportunities**\n\nThere is strong interest in exploring AI-driven communication and automation to improve customer engagement and reduce manual workload (36:25).\n\n- **Max Longin** proposed developing an AI sales assistant capable of conversational texting to answer common questions and engage leads before handing off to sales reps (36:40).\n- The current website chatbot handles limited guided responses from a fixed knowledge base; expanding this with AI and connecting it to dynamic data would enhance user experience (38:47).\n- Automation of lead engagement through HubSpot workflows, including SMS drip campaigns, is under consideration to increase touchpoints and improve conversion rates (35:50).\n- The team acknowledged that while AI bots may be recognized as non-human, quick and contextually accurate answers over text are highly valued by customers (39:19).\n\n## **Implementation and Next Steps**\n\nThe group agreed to continue refining workflows and integrations with HubSpot expertise, focusing on process clarity, automation, and better data utilization (43:04).\n\n- **Colin Costigan** and team will work on exporting and templating HubSpot configurations to enable easier deployment across new instances or platforms, aiming for rapid replication (25:29).\n- Discussions will continue on improving the manual signup process and contract capture, with potential solutions to be presented in the coming days by **Stan Reznik’s** team (14:16).\n- The team emphasized the need for ongoing iteration and expertise in sales workflow design to fully leverage HubSpot’s capabilities beyond just integration (44:19).\n- The call concluded with plans to resume the conversation next week, focusing on gaps identified and potential tech-enabled improvements to sales and member management processes (01:02:02).","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot","Data Track","CRM Integration","Aircall","Lead Management","Sales Workflows"],"overview":"- **CRM Integration:** HubSpot integrates with Meta ads and website forms for seamless lead capture and automatic drip campaigns.\n\n- **Manual Processes:** Lead transfer to Data Track is manual, causing inefficiencies and requiring duplicate data entry.\n\n- **Calling & Texting Volume:** Sales reps make 60-100 calls daily, totaling over 2,000 calls weekly, with manual texting efforts as well.\n\n- **Data Track Limitations:** Lacks CRM functions, leading to manual lead account creation and contract signing, increasing administrative workload.\n\n- **Analytics Needs:** Improved visibility into sales performance and churn metrics is essential to enhance decision-making and retention strategies.\n\n- **AI Opportunities:** Exploring AI-driven communication tools to streamline engagement and reduce manual workloads is a priority moving forward.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nProvide meeting recording to all participants (01:01:45)\nAssist with exporting HubSpot property configurations and workflows for duplication or integration (16:40)\n\n**Milan Wagner**\nSupport modification and presentation of HubSpot sales process workflows (21:00)\nManage and track outbound call/text campaign metrics and sales rep activity (50:25)\n\n**Yefei Jin**\nCoordinate feedback and review proposed signup workflow improvements from Stan Reznik and others (14:45)\n\n**Stan Reznik**\nDraft and share enhanced manual phone signup workflow proposals with Powerhouse team (14:40)\nContinue conversation on optimizing sales and retention workflows with Powerhouse (01:02:00)\n\n**Max Longin**\nAnalyze potential for AI-driven texting assistant integrated with HubSpot and Data Track (36:00)\nExplore development of integration app for replication of HubSpot sales process in other gyms/platforms (22:30)\n\n**Wyatt Callow**\nInvestigate sales call and member engagement data collection improvements (30:05)\n"},"duration":63.18000030517578,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":1,"name":"Yefei Jin"},{"id":2,"name":"Milan Wagner"},{"id":3,"name":"Stan Reznik"},{"id":4,"name":"Max Longin"},{"id":5,"name":"Stan Reznik"},{"id":6,"name":"Wyatt Callow"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":162.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":161.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hi.","index":1,"end_time":163.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How''s it going?","index":2,"end_time":164.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":163.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good.","index":3,"end_time":166.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":165.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Friday?","index":4,"end_time":185.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I feel like it''s the busiest day of this week sometimes.","index":5,"end_time":192.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":186.71,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":6,"end_time":222.16,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":221.6,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Hello.","index":7,"end_time":223.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":223.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":8,"end_time":225.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":224.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How are you guys doing?","index":9,"end_time":227.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":225.92,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"All right.","index":10,"end_time":228.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How about yourself?","index":11,"end_time":229.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":228.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, well, it is Friday, so.","index":12,"end_time":232.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":230.01,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Yes.","index":13,"end_time":232.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":232.49,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"We inherently get three.","index":14,"end_time":234.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":233.45,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Three extra points for our well being factor here.","index":15,"end_time":239.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":234.89,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"There you go.","index":16,"end_time":240.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":239.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, looks like we''ve got a couple more folks joining from our side, so we''ll give them a second.","index":17,"end_time":247.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":242.09,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Hi, everyone.","index":18,"end_time":253.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":252.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How we doing?","index":19,"end_time":254.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":253.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Hey, Milan.","index":20,"end_time":255.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":254.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let me ping Max and Wyatt and hopefully we can.","index":21,"end_time":274.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":267.44,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"We can get rolling.","index":22,"end_time":275.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":274.4,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Milan, is yuff joining?","index":23,"end_time":277.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":276.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think he is not totally sure though.","index":24,"end_time":284.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":279.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Hey, Stan, you pay.","index":25,"end_time":326.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":324.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":26,"end_time":326.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":326.11,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Morning.","index":27,"end_time":329.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":329.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I guess I''m trying to corral my troops here.","index":28,"end_time":336.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":332.8,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"One sec.","index":29,"end_time":337.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":336.72,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Yeah, I think Max was definitely planning and attending.","index":30,"end_time":342.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":337.28,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Not just planning, attending.","index":31,"end_time":344.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":343.52,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Okay, here we go.","index":32,"end_time":347.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":345.44,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Still good.","index":33,"end_time":348.16,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":347.44,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Max, are you.","index":34,"end_time":349.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":348.48,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Are you aware of Wyatt''s itinerary?","index":35,"end_time":352.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":350.4,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"I''m not sure he.","index":36,"end_time":354.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":353.12,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"He was on the invite.","index":37,"end_time":355.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":354.08,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"I''m not sure if he was.","index":38,"end_time":356,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":355.08,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t know if he''ll be able to make it, but we can.","index":39,"end_time":359.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":356.8,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"We can get rolling.","index":40,"end_time":360.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":359.92,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So we really appreciate you guys jumping on an ethe.","index":41,"end_time":365.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":362.29,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Thanks for setting it up and thanks for the write up too.","index":42,"end_time":369.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":365.93,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, it was great.","index":43,"end_time":371.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":370.45,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"It was awesome.","index":44,"end_time":374.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":373.33,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So would love to basically get as much in the weeds and details as you guys are willing to share.","index":45,"end_time":385.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":375.17,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Maybe even starting from, like, can we see this thing in action?","index":46,"end_time":390.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":387.03,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Like, how.","index":47,"end_time":391.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":390.91,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"How is it that you guys are using it and clearly like the.","index":48,"end_time":395.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":391.39,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"I understood what you were going for ife and also really feel your pain on not being able to get there fully.","index":49,"end_time":404.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":396.31,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":50,"end_time":406.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":406.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"From a customer journey perspective, because I think the only way to get that done is to have something that is actually going to control the whole entire customer journey from start to finish.","index":51,"end_time":416.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":408.07,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":52,"end_time":417.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":417.57,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"That unfortunately doesn''t exist yet.","index":53,"end_time":420.61,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":417.77,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, we can.","index":54,"end_time":421.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":420.61,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I gave this groups a little bit of context to this call and Colin and Nina Here are the.","index":55,"end_time":427.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":422.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is the agency we contracted with to build out the HubSpot setup and connect to Data Track.","index":56,"end_time":434.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I think.","index":57,"end_time":437.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":436.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":58,"end_time":439.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":439.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you.","index":59,"end_time":439.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":439.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Should we just.","index":60,"end_time":440.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":439.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you want to start with.","index":61,"end_time":441.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":440.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You said you want to see how it works?","index":62,"end_time":444.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":442.37,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you Want to see HubSpot?","index":63,"end_time":445.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":444.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you want to just.","index":64,"end_time":446.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":445.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Should we just screen share that or.","index":65,"end_time":447.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":446.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, honestly, like, given the whole.","index":66,"end_time":450.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":448.21,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"The whole workflow, like how.","index":67,"end_time":453.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":450.53,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Where can things start?","index":68,"end_time":455.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":453.89,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"You know, let''s start with HubSpot if we can.","index":69,"end_time":458.209,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":455.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s a bit easier to conceptualize.","index":70,"end_time":460.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":458.209,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And Data track is all API.","index":71,"end_time":462.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":460.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s like all.","index":72,"end_time":463.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":462.57,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And looking at Data track is like.","index":73,"end_time":465.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":464.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I know, it gives me, like, heartache, like looking at the interface A little bit.","index":74,"end_time":471.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":466.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But the HubSpot will be easier because that operates like a traditional CRM and we can kind of point to how, like what''s triggering that?","index":75,"end_time":479.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":471.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that something you can screen share?","index":76,"end_time":481.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":480.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, like just start with the most basic like lead page or list view.","index":77,"end_time":487.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":481.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":78,"end_time":489.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":488.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Give me two seconds here.","index":79,"end_time":491.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":489.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And so the other thing as Ron is pulling this up, so there are obviously there are multiple ways of how leads kind of end up right in the.","index":80,"end_time":501.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":492.82,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"In HubSpot.","index":81,"end_time":502.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":501.79,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So did you guys basically integrate like landing pages into your website and into your social media?","index":82,"end_time":508.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":503.07,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Is that how you guys did it?","index":83,"end_time":510.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":508.83,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":84,"end_time":512.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":511.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Colin, do you want to speak to that?","index":85,"end_time":513.429,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":512.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like how does the paid ad side connect and how does the website.","index":86,"end_time":516.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.429,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, Meta is directly integrated with HubSpot and website forms.","index":87,"end_time":521.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":516.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We replaced on the squarespace site with just HubSpot forms.","index":88,"end_time":524.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":521.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So they''re directly integrated as well.","index":89,"end_time":526.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":524.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so we''ll be able to pull those up really quick or are they just gonna like open when the website is the case?","index":90,"end_time":536.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":527.67,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, why don''t you.","index":91,"end_time":536.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":536.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, can you open go to our website just as an example?","index":92,"end_time":540.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":537.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, guys, I think, I think maybe just like really just a full user.","index":93,"end_time":546.35,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":542.71,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Journey through this would be, would be awesome to see kind of.","index":94,"end_time":550.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":546.35,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Through the most.","index":95,"end_time":552.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":552.4,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Okay, so this is our website over here.","index":96,"end_time":556.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":552.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There''s two different forms you want to record.","index":97,"end_time":560.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":558.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, you already are.","index":98,"end_time":561.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":560.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Great.","index":99,"end_time":562.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":561.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have the join now form which is right here.","index":100,"end_time":568.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":564.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we have our different membership options.","index":101,"end_time":571.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":569.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So Fort Lauderdale, Miami, and then Premier, which is including both a member.","index":102,"end_time":579.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":572.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Let''s say our prospect wants to join the Miami location.","index":103,"end_time":582.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":579.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"They would click this button here, it would fill out their information.","index":104,"end_time":586.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":582.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"They would have to agree.","index":105,"end_time":587.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":586.33,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"This is a HubSpot form, right?","index":106,"end_time":590.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":588.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Correct?","index":107,"end_time":591.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":590.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, this is a, this is the HubSpot form online.","index":108,"end_time":594.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":591.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And we have two of them.","index":109,"end_time":597.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":596.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"One for the join online now link and then the scheduled visit link.","index":110,"end_time":601.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":597.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So anyway, they would submit, they get this thank you message and then they would go to this page which is the data track, like online platform where they can just sign up.","index":111,"end_time":618.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":602.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So they would then select again their membership option.","index":112,"end_time":622.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":618.45,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"They would click next and then they would fill out all their information here.","index":113,"end_time":629.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":624.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So do they double enter some of.","index":114,"end_time":633.56,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":632.08,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"This stuff like first and they''re done?","index":115,"end_time":635.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":633.56,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Yes.","index":116,"end_time":636.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":636.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, they''re double entering in the on the HubSpot form first and then they have to do it again here.","index":117,"end_time":643.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":636.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so they would do it here.","index":118,"end_time":646.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":644.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Let me see if I have to put my card information.","index":119,"end_time":650.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":648.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":120,"end_time":651.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":650.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I can just go to the next step here.","index":121,"end_time":654.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":651.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Two seconds.","index":122,"end_time":655.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":654.97,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And, and this is, this is data track.","index":123,"end_time":657.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":655.77,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":124,"end_time":657.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":657.65,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like you''re basically like, you want to lead in your CRM at the same time as they''re signing up.","index":125,"end_time":663.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":657.89,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Like if they actually want to go through that journey.","index":126,"end_time":665.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":663.93,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Correct, yeah.","index":127,"end_time":669.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":667.21,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So in case they, they, in case they don''t complete something right.","index":128,"end_time":674.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":669.29,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Then you can pull up and call them.","index":129,"end_time":676.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":674.97,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right, Right.","index":130,"end_time":677.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":676.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They get, they start to get the drip campaign, the emails right away.","index":131,"end_time":681.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":677.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Most, most of our leads don''t come in through this way for the reason you mentioned double entering and website not great.","index":132,"end_time":690.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":681.37,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But they, they do come in through the lead, the paid ads.","index":133,"end_time":693.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":690.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So once they come go into, once they fill out a form on Instagram, it shows up in help spot.","index":134,"end_time":699.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":693.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that, that is the more common way that we do business.","index":135,"end_time":702.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":699.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not through what Milan is showing you here.","index":136,"end_time":705.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":702.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But this is like one of the possible flows that obviously could be better because we like to direct people to the website.","index":137,"end_time":711.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":705.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But all this is just.","index":138,"end_time":712.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":711.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And ebay, if, if they go to.","index":139,"end_time":714.81,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":712.73,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Let''S say if this is coming from like a Facebook ad or something.","index":140,"end_time":718.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":714.81,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Is, is this flow the same like.","index":141,"end_time":720.89,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":718.57,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"To first to the HubSpot form, then to data track for actual sign up.","index":142,"end_time":727.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":720.89,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Do you, can you share that?","index":143,"end_time":732.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":730.97,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Colin?","index":144,"end_time":732.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":732.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Can you share your screen of what that looks like?","index":145,"end_time":734.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":732.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Which flow the HubSpot, the Meta to HubSpot and walk through that.","index":146,"end_time":743.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":736.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But what you just saw is like typical payment stuff.","index":147,"end_time":748.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":743.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But also you don''t sign a contract.","index":148,"end_time":751.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":749.49,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"There''s no contract signature.","index":149,"end_time":753.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":752.05,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"There is.","index":150,"end_time":755.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":753.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So once you put in your card information there would just be like a checkbox which would be signing the contract.","index":151,"end_time":760.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":755.57,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":152,"end_time":763.38,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":763.02,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like when they do it that way, when they actually do a full sign up online, then yeah, they, then the contract is signed.","index":153,"end_time":770.94,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":763.38,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Correct.","index":154,"end_time":772.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":771.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And but if, if they go through the traditional kind of lead.","index":155,"end_time":777.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":773.82,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":156,"end_time":778.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":778.38,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So and then you basically like, you talk to them and you go, okay, let me send you the stuff.","index":157,"end_time":783.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":778.859,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right?","index":158,"end_time":784.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":783.9,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"What, what happens then?","index":159,"end_time":785.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":784.26,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So we don''t, so if it''s on the phone for example, and we''re signing them up, we don''t send them any link or anything.","index":160,"end_time":792.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":787.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We take the card information over the phone, we set them up manually and then they have to come in in person to sign their agreement at the front desk on one of our digital like veri phones.","index":161,"end_time":806.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":793.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There''s no way to like send the agreement.","index":162,"end_time":810.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":807.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, data track does not have capability.","index":163,"end_time":812.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":810.22,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Correct.","index":164,"end_time":813.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":813.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":165,"end_time":816.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":815.58,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"My suspicion is that even if we could do electronic signatures, people may not do it.","index":166,"end_time":823.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":817.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":167,"end_time":824.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":824.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we take the card, like some of it is a process like investigation, like what is a user likely going to do to pay the card?","index":168,"end_time":832.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":824.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then you tell them we Got to sign this on your own time.","index":169,"end_time":834.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":832.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m not going to do it.","index":170,"end_time":835.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":834.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it might be like they have to.","index":171,"end_time":837.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":835.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There is something.","index":172,"end_time":838.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":837.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It does happen when they show up.","index":173,"end_time":840.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":838.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"However, we miss people all the time because the flag that notifies us is so easily missed in the system.","index":174,"end_time":847.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":840.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we''d have hundreds of people without like liability form signed up, signed, no contract, literally signed because HubSpot or Data Track misses it.","index":175,"end_time":856.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":847.79,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we have a couple of ideas.","index":176,"end_time":859.23,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":856.19,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"We''ll probably even show you kind of which way we''re.","index":177,"end_time":861.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":859.23,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"We''re thinking of going here to kind of alleviate this to basically give you the ability to have a much better, you know, let''s call it on the phone or manual signup process.","index":178,"end_time":871.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":861.35,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Should you choose to do that, do it that way.","index":179,"end_time":873.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":871.87,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"So maybe, maybe in the next few days we can run this by you and see if that kind of is it or if we''re missing anything.","index":180,"end_time":883.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":874.19,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s great.","index":181,"end_time":885.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":884.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Colin, you were just screen sharing the.","index":182,"end_time":886.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":885.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Did you see the.","index":183,"end_time":888.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":887.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This is The Meta to HubSpot set up.","index":184,"end_time":891.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":889.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":185,"end_time":891.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":891.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So all the mapping is set up to go directly to the contact on submission.","index":186,"end_time":895.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":891.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So this is just direct.","index":187,"end_time":898.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":897.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This isn''t working through make or anything.","index":188,"end_time":900.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":898.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s just direct integration between Meta and HubSpot.","index":189,"end_time":902.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":900.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, that, that''s actually pretty cool.","index":190,"end_time":906.84,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":904.76,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So metal Hopspot.","index":191,"end_time":914.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":912.92,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Got it.","index":192,"end_time":915,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":914.48,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And then from, from here, you don''t, you don''t port that.","index":193,"end_time":919.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":916.04,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So they could say I actually work, I work this lead and there''s not like a, oh, I can just, you know, take this and sell it in Data Track.","index":194,"end_time":929.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":920.04,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":195,"end_time":930.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":929.95,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"You have to go to Data Track, basically enter all of this stuff into Data Track, right?","index":196,"end_time":936.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":930.43,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":197,"end_time":938.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":937.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that''s the biggest headache of this whole thing.","index":198,"end_time":940.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":938.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Milan, if you wanted to speak to that.","index":199,"end_time":942.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":940.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Data Track has a lot of limitations.","index":200,"end_time":944.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":943.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":201,"end_time":947.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":946.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":202,"end_time":947.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":947.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, it''s a very manual process when, I mean, we''re collecting payment through the phone, for example, when we''re.","index":203,"end_time":958.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":947.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We''re doing.","index":204,"end_time":959.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":959.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Or when a prospect signs these like waiver forms online or even in person.","index":205,"end_time":964.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":960.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s also not creating a lead account on Data Track anymore.","index":206,"end_time":969.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":964.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It used to do that, but what that means is that the rep then also has to fill out their, their name and all the general information again, manually there too.","index":207,"end_time":980.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":969.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":208,"end_time":983.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":982.88,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":209,"end_time":987.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":986.56,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Is this hotspot configuration?","index":210,"end_time":993.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":989.6,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Colin and Nina, like, do you think that this is something that can be kind of encapsulated and deployed like two different tenants, Ours?","index":211,"end_time":1006.16,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":995.76,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"I''m not sure what you mean.","index":212,"end_time":1007.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1006.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if we, let''s say, decided to have an integration into kind of our platform that we''re building.","index":213,"end_time":1018.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1008.35,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":214,"end_time":1019.23,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1018.83,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And we said, hey, before we build our own CRM, we actually want to use HubSpot as a kind of a stopgap to be, you know, while we''re kind of in process.","index":215,"end_time":1030.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1019.71,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Is it easy to take another configuration in Hotspot?","index":216,"end_time":1036.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1032.11,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Because I actually have no experience working with HubSpot.","index":217,"end_time":1039.55,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1036.75,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"I am sorry to say, I''m a Salesforce guy, but I''m recovering.","index":218,"end_time":1043.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1039.71,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So is it easy to take the configuration and say like, I want this configuration of HubSpot deployed in different HubSpot tenant?","index":219,"end_time":1056.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1046.35,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":220,"end_time":1057.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1056.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s several different ways to do it.","index":221,"end_time":1058.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1057.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean at the simplest form, we can export every single property from HubSpot pretty easily into a spreadsheet.","index":222,"end_time":1064.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1058.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But you can also develop custom apps, API integrations, really anything that''s needed if you have, I''m not sure the capability I imagine by the way you''re speaking of it, with your platform being able to have two way syncs and like a listen and ascend for APIs.","index":223,"end_time":1079.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1064.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":224,"end_time":1081.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1080.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"HubSpot, we can build a custom app that integrates and connects those systems.","index":225,"end_time":1084.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1081.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is it, correct me if I''m wrong here, Data Track doesn''t have web hooks.","index":226,"end_time":1094.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1087.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have to do syncs every like five minutes.","index":227,"end_time":1099.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1096.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So yeah, there''s, there''s different variables and it''s also, yeah, it''s a get post instead of a clean like webhook.","index":228,"end_time":1108.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1100.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":229,"end_time":1109.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1108.62,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"It''s very archaic.","index":230,"end_time":1111.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1109.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so there''s no way for HubSpot to know anything about like what, what, what is happening in Data Track.","index":231,"end_time":1120.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1113.11,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"You have to go get it.","index":232,"end_time":1122.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1121.03,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Well, I mean it''s a, it''s a get that''s happening through make operations.","index":233,"end_time":1126.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1122.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":234,"end_time":1127.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1127.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So, so you, so you guys control the frequency of the polling based on.","index":235,"end_time":1131.63,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1127.99,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Just the business desires.","index":236,"end_time":1135.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1131.63,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"And I, I, I presume that it.","index":237,"end_time":1138.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1135.15,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"There''S no cost associated with like how.","index":238,"end_time":1141.68,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1139.08,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Often you go pulling Data track or.","index":239,"end_time":1144.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1141.68,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"No, there, there is cost.","index":240,"end_time":1146.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1144.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s minimal.","index":241,"end_time":1147.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1146.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I got cost of Colin, you said was around like 3, $300 or so.","index":242,"end_time":1151.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1147.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re at 500,000 operations a month right now.","index":243,"end_time":1155.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1151.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But we had to tick that up last month because we had to fix a lot of what was previously built into make.","index":244,"end_time":1163.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1156.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We had to, it was built by another team and we had to just go in and kind of, it wasn''t consolidated as it should have been.","index":245,"end_time":1171.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1163.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There was a lot of extra operations that were happening and wasting spend, so we had to up it.","index":246,"end_time":1176.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1171.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But we can likely go back down once you know, everything is all cleaned up.","index":247,"end_time":1182.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1176.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Colin, but to be clear, you''re talking about the make Spend.","index":248,"end_time":1186.57,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1183.33,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Is there, is there a Data Track API fee that they charge you depending.","index":249,"end_time":1192.37,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1186.57,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"On the frequency of the requests that you''re making?","index":250,"end_time":1194.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1192.37,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Yifei, that would be on your end.","index":251,"end_time":1196.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1195.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not sure if Data Track is charging you guys.","index":252,"end_time":1198.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1196.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t think they are.","index":253,"end_time":1198.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1198.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I, I don''t know.","index":254,"end_time":1200.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1199.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":255,"end_time":1201.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1200.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not that I''m aware of.","index":256,"end_time":1202.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1201.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They gave us like a swagger site where we.","index":257,"end_time":1208.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1202.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"With the API.","index":258,"end_time":1209.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1208.85,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, with the APIs and we just pull all of the, the relevant API calls from that.","index":259,"end_time":1214.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1209.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":260,"end_time":1216.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1216.13,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"So here''s just an example of the HTTP request that''s going through and then routing, parsing and then making a decision.","index":261,"end_time":1229.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1220.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But so this is for the Miami Club.","index":262,"end_time":1231.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1229.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We consolidated this down to, I think it''s six total operations.","index":263,"end_time":1237.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1233.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can see previously there was many, many more before we took over.","index":264,"end_time":1241.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1237.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":265,"end_time":1246.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1245.91,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"And I try to give a, just a high level overview of these in that document as well with some screenshots.","index":266,"end_time":1251.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1246.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, this is great.","index":267,"end_time":1253.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1252.31,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"This actually makes, it makes a lot of sense.","index":268,"end_time":1256.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1254.15,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"This part wasn''t like you guys did like had to go in and kind of make some corrections, but correct me if I''m wrong, like this column.","index":269,"end_time":1270.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1258.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Would you say like if you were asked to build an integration with another into HubSpot and you could do it from scratch from the beginning?","index":270,"end_time":1278.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1270.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This isn''t where we spent the most of our time.","index":271,"end_time":1281.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1279.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Most of the development hours.","index":272,"end_time":1283.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1281.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":273,"end_time":1284.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1284,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Have been configuration inside HubSpot.","index":274,"end_time":1287.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1284.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":275,"end_time":1288.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1287.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It just was like, how do we, how is our business team going to use that data as opposed to like the integration itself?","index":276,"end_time":1296.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1290.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It wasn''t a big effort.","index":277,"end_time":1298.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1296.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":278,"end_time":1298.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1298.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":279,"end_time":1298.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1298.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Most of the time is working with Milan on like sales process and workflow changes.","index":280,"end_time":1302.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1298.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we tapped into like originally we weren''t planning to use HubSpot''s lead property because that was in beta.","index":281,"end_time":1309.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1302.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But then we talked about it and we set that up.","index":282,"end_time":1312,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1309.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So now we have leads and contacts as two separate objects inside of HubSpot, but they are connected and they update each other.","index":283,"end_time":1319.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1312.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the bulk of our time was spent on just like workflow or process changes.","index":284,"end_time":1323.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1319.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that was actually my question.","index":285,"end_time":1326.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1325.53,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So let''s say we''re deploying a new club, right.","index":286,"end_time":1331.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1327.85,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And they are using Salesforce or something else.","index":287,"end_time":1335.49,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1331.97,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":288,"end_time":1335.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1335.49,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And we''re saying, hey, we have a better mousetrap, but you gotta abandon Salesforce.","index":289,"end_time":1339.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1335.65,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"That is okay.","index":290,"end_time":1340.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1340.09,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Don''t want that.","index":291,"end_time":1342.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1341.21,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"We have a deployment that you can take and let''s say it''s completely clean.","index":292,"end_time":1349.37,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1344.17,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"There''s nothing there.","index":293,"end_time":1350.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1349.37,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Can you.","index":294,"end_time":1353.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1352.96,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Is there a template configuration for HubSpot where you can take and say this is the process deploy.","index":295,"end_time":1360.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1353.4,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, everything in HubSpot is all field mapping, so you control every variable that comes into it.","index":296,"end_time":1367.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1361.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It also has, like in your example, Salesforce, it has direct integrations with Salesforce that we can tap into.","index":297,"end_time":1373.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1367.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So there''s, there''s a few different ways that we can tap into that.","index":298,"end_time":1375.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1373.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":299,"end_time":1377.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1377.37,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So there is a way to deploy a template, like into a clean.","index":300,"end_time":1380.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1377.57,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And what form does it take?","index":301,"end_time":1384.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1382.33,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":302,"end_time":1384.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1384.13,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"For something is that.","index":303,"end_time":1386.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1385.53,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Can you deploy.","index":304,"end_time":1387.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1386.73,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Can we develop an app that says once you install it, it configures HubSpot?","index":305,"end_time":1391.37,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1387.53,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"We can develop apps and just define custom variables for them to point to or to read.","index":306,"end_time":1398.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1391.849,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It also accepts, you know, if it''s just like a bunch of data, it could do CSVs, you know, kind of anything in that range of complexity.","index":307,"end_time":1406.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1398.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":308,"end_time":1407.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1406.76,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So that''s the integration, but the actual business workflow, Hopspot works.","index":309,"end_time":1411.52,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1407.12,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":310,"end_time":1411.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1411.52,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like Milan, like for you, like when a lead comes in, I want that to be kind of in my.","index":311,"end_time":1416.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1411.8,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Kind of in my, you know, action or work plans for my.","index":312,"end_time":1421.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1416.84,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"For my salespeople.","index":313,"end_time":1423.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1421.44,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":314,"end_time":1423.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1423.28,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So how does, how is that work plan defined?","index":315,"end_time":1425.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1423.56,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":316,"end_time":1426.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1426.28,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like, what sort of SLA am I expecting, like that going to stop?","index":317,"end_time":1430.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1426.68,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":318,"end_time":1430.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1430.6,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":319,"end_time":1433.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1432.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Everything will be built into workflows.","index":320,"end_time":1435.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1433.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So those are all here.","index":321,"end_time":1437.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1436.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we have basically triggers of when a workflow starts and then the branches that everything will go down.","index":322,"end_time":1443.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1437.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That is where you''ll find the Most information on SOP, inside of HubSpot.","index":323,"end_time":1447.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1443.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":324,"end_time":1449.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1448.97,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So there it''s a workflow, but that requires probably the configuration of your contact objects or your lead objects, opportunities and so on and so forth.","index":325,"end_time":1462.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1449.41,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":326,"end_time":1462.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1462.69,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like, has that been customized or are you guys using just like a stock?","index":327,"end_time":1467.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1462.95,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"All the workflows are custom built.","index":328,"end_time":1469.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1468.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The workflows, yes.","index":329,"end_time":1471.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1470.31,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"But what about the objects?","index":330,"end_time":1472.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1471.27,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Are you guys using custom objects of any sort?","index":331,"end_time":1474.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1472.03,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, there''s many custom objects.","index":332,"end_time":1475.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1474.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, as simple as like, club name is a custom object.","index":333,"end_time":1478.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1475.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But like the ones that come out of the box for HubSpot are more first name, last name, email address, company, all that sort of stuff.","index":334,"end_time":1484.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1478.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, like, well, we''ll probably need to spend some time kind of like digesting that piece of it.","index":335,"end_time":1495.52,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1486.55,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Stan, you see where I''m leading, right?","index":336,"end_time":1499.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1498.24,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":337,"end_time":1501.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1500.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No, for sure.","index":338,"end_time":1502.76,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1501.6,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Creating an easy process around this would be.","index":339,"end_time":1505.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1502.76,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Would be valuable.","index":340,"end_time":1508.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1507.36,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":341,"end_time":1509.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1508.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So here''s all properties and then it''s split up by the type of objects and we can export any of these.","index":342,"end_time":1514.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1509.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Mm.","index":343,"end_time":1515.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1515.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How long do you think it would take, like to start from scratch and say, hey, we want to deploy this configuration onto a new HubSpot instance.","index":344,"end_time":1528.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1520,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"From one HubSpot instance to another, it''d be very quick.","index":345,"end_time":1532.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1529.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean I don''t know the exact time, but everything''s built.","index":346,"end_time":1538.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1532.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So HubSpot to HubSpot, it would be very quick.","index":347,"end_time":1540.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1538.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hubs HubSpot into your platform?","index":348,"end_time":1542.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1540.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not sure.","index":349,"end_time":1543.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1542.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, for our platform we would just.","index":350,"end_time":1547.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1545.61,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"I think we would work with you on building, building kind of an integration kind of app for HubSpot so that it can just get done.","index":351,"end_time":1554.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1547.85,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":352,"end_time":1557.289,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1556.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The configuring of the configuration of the sales process and kind of setting up these standard SOPs for clubs, that''s.","index":353,"end_time":1566.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1558.17,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"That''s what''s on my mind.","index":354,"end_time":1568.34,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1567.38,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And then where we go from there, I think that''s.","index":355,"end_time":1573.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1569.7,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Those are going to be the questions, but rhetorical right now.","index":356,"end_time":1579.3,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1573.66,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":357,"end_time":1580.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1579.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":358,"end_time":1584.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1583.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s a. I''m not enough.","index":359,"end_time":1589.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1586.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Other gyms would have a system like this.","index":360,"end_time":1591.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1589.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have a phone dialer, right.","index":361,"end_time":1593.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1591.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Called Air Call that when someone calls us, it also routes into HubSpot.","index":362,"end_time":1600.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1593.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Part of our work was also looking at which dialer is going to be most easy to integrate into HubSpot and there are dozens of dialers in the world that does something here like Colin or Milan.","index":363,"end_time":1613.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1600.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Did you want to speak to any of like how that works inside HubSpot and does it touch data track in any way with.","index":364,"end_time":1620.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1613.56,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"With the Air call?","index":365,"end_time":1622.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1620.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, you''ve been knee deep in Air.","index":366,"end_time":1625.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1623.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, Air Call doesn''t touch data track.","index":367,"end_time":1629.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1625.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It was a simple integration with HubSpot.","index":368,"end_time":1634.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1631.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Whenever a point of contact, so whether it be a text or a call is done on aircall to a prospect, it gets synced to the actual Prospect account on HubSpot under like its activities and you''ll be able to see the call, the call recording any notes, whatever the text message was, etc.","index":369,"end_time":1658.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1637.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Emails are going to be done off of HubSpot, not off of aircall and then in terms of like call queue.","index":370,"end_time":1667.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1659.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So let''s say that this prospect doesn''t exist in HubSpot and it''s calling the, the sales department''s phone number.","index":371,"end_time":1675.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1667.25,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It acts as like a first come, first serve situation.","index":372,"end_time":1679.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1676.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So all the reps, as soon as they see the call, first person who answers it gets the lead.","index":373,"end_time":1683.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1679.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But then it''s a manual process in creating that lead.","index":374,"end_time":1686.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1683.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So there''s like, there''s a HubSpot hyperlink on aircall that you can click it and it''ll start creating a lead, a Prospect account on HubSpot.","index":375,"end_time":1699.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1686.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You just have to fill out the name and all the extra information in there.","index":376,"end_time":1703.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1699.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then that gets sent into the individual reps pipelines and then they can work that.","index":377,"end_time":1710.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1703.79,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We looked at maybe a couple others and this one was like by different people.","index":378,"end_time":1718.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1711.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It said this is the best one for HubSpot.","index":379,"end_time":1721.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1718.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I don''t, I can''t speak to like if we had more time to investigate what that could be, we may have picked another.","index":380,"end_time":1726.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1721.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we probably what picked us and a week or so, two weeks.","index":381,"end_time":1730.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1726.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It wasn''t even that.","index":382,"end_time":1731.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1730.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It wasn''t that long.","index":383,"end_time":1731.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1731.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We asked our HubSpot rep as well.","index":384,"end_time":1733.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1731.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What, from your experience, what works best with that system?","index":385,"end_time":1736.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1733.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So what happens when all the seller reps are busy and Nicole is coming in?","index":386,"end_time":1743.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1739.4,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"What happens?","index":387,"end_time":1744.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1743.4,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Just, does it just ring?","index":388,"end_time":1746.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1744.28,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Is there a queue?","index":389,"end_time":1748.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1747.16,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So yeah, you can format their experience on the call.","index":390,"end_time":1753.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1749,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it would ring like one, maybe two times.","index":391,"end_time":1757.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1754.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I am.","index":392,"end_time":1758.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1758.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Then I also receive a call if it''s not answered and if nobody answers it, then it goes to missed call with a voicemail.","index":393,"end_time":1766.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1758.91,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then as soon as the reps are available again, they''ll reach back out to that prospect.","index":394,"end_time":1772.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1767.59,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so there''s not like a virtual receptionist or like, hey, please hold somebody, we''ll deal with you shortly.","index":395,"end_time":1780.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1773.91,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Like none of that.","index":396,"end_time":1781.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1780.79,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"You can create that.","index":397,"end_time":1784.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1783.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yes, you can create that on the air call workflow.","index":398,"end_time":1788.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1784.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It doesn''t currently exist in the process, but the capability in air call is there.","index":399,"end_time":1791.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1788.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so to just have an auto attendant or a call queue, basically, yeah.","index":400,"end_time":1798.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1792.91,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"You can do phone trees, all sorts of things.","index":401,"end_time":1800.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1798.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so that exists.","index":402,"end_time":1802.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1801.15,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"But as far as like a virtual receptionist isn''t like an actual AI bottom talking to the customer.","index":403,"end_time":1808.72,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1802.83,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"That.","index":404,"end_time":1809.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1809.36,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"That does not exist or that also exists.","index":405,"end_time":1811.52,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1809.68,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"I don''t believe that exists.","index":406,"end_time":1813.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1812.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":407,"end_time":1815.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1815.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Hey Milan, quick question for you.","index":408,"end_time":1817.56,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1815.96,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"First of all, good to see you again.","index":409,"end_time":1818.56,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1817.56,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Sorry to join late.","index":410,"end_time":1819.44,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1818.56,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"When, when that call is missed and you get that list, is that you handling the assignment of what rep that''s going to go to or does it go to kind of a general bucket that any sales rep can pull from?","index":411,"end_time":1830.16,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1820.48,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"I don''t get the list.","index":412,"end_time":1831.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1830.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I, I received a call.","index":413,"end_time":1833.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1831.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So for example, it goes to the call queue.","index":414,"end_time":1836.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1834.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All three reps don''t answer it.","index":415,"end_time":1838.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1836.85,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It goes to another like please hold workflow.","index":416,"end_time":1842.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1839.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then I receive the call and then I''m able to then answer the call as like a rep, as a fallback rep.","index":417,"end_time":1849.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1842.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, but then if it actually gets missed, then it goes into the missed call bliss.","index":418,"end_time":1857.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1851.09,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right, that the reps basically then that whoever frees up first goes and.","index":419,"end_time":1862.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1858.05,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Exactly, exactly.","index":420,"end_time":1864.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1862.39,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So that''s the inbound workflow.","index":421,"end_time":1868.15,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1866.27,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"What about the outbound workflows?","index":422,"end_time":1869.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1868.15,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"How does that work?","index":423,"end_time":1870.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1869.95,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"What do you mean by that?","index":424,"end_time":1875.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1873.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So do you guys cold call?","index":425,"end_time":1876.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1875.39,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"We do a lot of cold calling.","index":426,"end_time":1878.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1877.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":427,"end_time":1879.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1878.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So what they do is they have pipelines on HubSpot that they just call on a regular basis and there''s hyperlinks on HubSpot that they can just click and it''ll just, it''ll just initiate the call, basically on the air call and there you go.","index":428,"end_time":1895.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1879.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it''s not a classic auto dialer.","index":429,"end_time":1896.63,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1895.07,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"I guess you''re not using it as a classic auto dialer in the sense.","index":430,"end_time":1899.55,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1896.63,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"That actually tries to get the, you know, the, the other customer on the phone automatically using some automation means and then rings the.","index":431,"end_time":1910.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1899.55,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Well, the.","index":432,"end_time":1911.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1910.67,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right, right.","index":433,"end_time":1912.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1911.39,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s more of a manual process.","index":434,"end_time":1914.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1912.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, I see.","index":435,"end_time":1916.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1914.58,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"If.","index":436,"end_time":1918.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1918.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Hey, I''m just curious, how many outbound calls do you.","index":437,"end_time":1920.7,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1918.34,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Do you typically make a week?","index":438,"end_time":1922.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1920.7,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"The wrecks tend to do about 60 to 100 calls a day.","index":439,"end_time":1930.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1925.78,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"There''s seven reps. Give me two seconds.","index":440,"end_time":1936.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1931.54,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"About 2,000, 2,000 plus calls.","index":441,"end_time":1941.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1939.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And how many text messages you think like high on 10,000.","index":442,"end_time":1944.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1941.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Double that person did 10,000 text messages.","index":443,"end_time":1949.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1945.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"One person did 15,000, 13,000.","index":444,"end_time":1952.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1950.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, he broke the limit.","index":445,"end_time":1954.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1952.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"They tend to do like around and that was like segments.","index":446,"end_time":1960.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1955.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"They tend to do about 2,000 to 3,000 texts a week.","index":447,"end_time":1964.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1960.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But they do, they do them manually.","index":448,"end_time":1966.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1964.69,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Correct.","index":449,"end_time":1968.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1967.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oi.","index":450,"end_time":1969.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1969.13,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":451,"end_time":1970.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1969.77,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":452,"end_time":1971.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1971.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What happens?","index":453,"end_time":1972.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1971.93,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Unwilling.","index":454,"end_time":1978.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1977.93,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So how does, how does that work?","index":455,"end_time":1981.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1979.609,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like Elite.","index":456,"end_time":1982.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1981.25,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Elite comes in or do people text you first?","index":457,"end_time":1985.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1982.17,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"No, we text them first.","index":458,"end_time":1988.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1986.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Unless they have our number saved and they, they give it out to someone as a referral or something like that, we tend to text them first.","index":459,"end_time":1995.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1988.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So if a lead comes in, first thing we do is we try and do five to six points of contact.","index":460,"end_time":2000.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1995.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Day one.","index":461,"end_time":2001.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2000.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we call text and email and then we''ll call text and email again later on in the day if we didn''t reach them.","index":462,"end_time":2009.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2001.86,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then after that there''s just a pipeline cadence that we follow and they just continuously text them throughout the month.","index":463,"end_time":2017.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2010.34,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And they, they do that for this month.","index":464,"end_time":2020.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2018.11,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Leads and then prior and last month''s leads, et cetera.","index":465,"end_time":2023.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2020.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":466,"end_time":2024.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2024.11,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So.","index":467,"end_time":2024.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2024.59,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And it''s something that is on the rep to remember or to get like, oh, I got a text on somebody.","index":468,"end_time":2030.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2024.99,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Oh, I got to text somebody.","index":469,"end_time":2031.47,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2030.27,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Correct.","index":470,"end_time":2032.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2032.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s on the rep, it''s on the sales managers and on myself to make sure that they''re doing it.","index":471,"end_time":2036.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2032.59,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, got it.","index":472,"end_time":2037.99,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2036.99,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"That, that is fascinating.","index":473,"end_time":2040.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2037.99,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"It''s gotta one small technicality.","index":474,"end_time":2045.32,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2041.39,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"When you guys collect a lead, do you guys.","index":475,"end_time":2048.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2045.56,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Do you guys gather text message consent?","index":476,"end_time":2051.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2048.52,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"We, I believe we do we used to with what''s it called, Ring DNA?","index":477,"end_time":2059.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2054.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I believe we do, yeah.","index":478,"end_time":2061.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2059.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well actually no, on the, on the waiver form, yes, they, they accept the terms and conditions.","index":479,"end_time":2068.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2061.96,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sorry, sorry guys, I''ll be right back.","index":480,"end_time":2070.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2068.44,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"On the waiver form online and in person they accept like the terms and conditions to receive SMS and for us to use their contact info.","index":481,"end_time":2079.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2071.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then on the first text message that we send out there''s also like a stop if you don''t want to receive anymore.","index":482,"end_time":2087.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2080.39,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":483,"end_time":2089.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2089.03,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And so, and so is the process similar then in terms of like when.","index":484,"end_time":2093.35,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2089.91,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"The reps are sending texts, they, they do them in batches and then just wait for responses and try to have conversations with the folks who.","index":485,"end_time":2103.239,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2093.35,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Some of the times.","index":486,"end_time":2105.759,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2104.999,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":487,"end_time":2106.199,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2105.759,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"When it''s, it depends on the type of lead.","index":488,"end_time":2109.999,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2106.519,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Right.","index":489,"end_time":2110.319,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2109.999,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So this month leads are going to be more tailored.","index":490,"end_time":2112.598,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2110.319,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we''re going to hopefully like generally with this month leads you, you have some kind of like rapport with them, you spoke to them at some point.","index":491,"end_time":2120.679,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2113.799,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean they''re going to be more tailored text messages for leads that are last month, prior month and, and have inquired in the past.","index":492,"end_time":2129.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2121.079,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s going to be more like those bash texts that it''s just like a promo text or come in for a day past deck, something like that.","index":493,"end_time":2135.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2129.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":494,"end_time":2137.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2137.14,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Okay, that''s, that''s interesting.","index":495,"end_time":2139.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2137.86,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"I''d be very curious to see how much optimization it feels like.","index":496,"end_time":2144.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2139.54,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"There''s, there''s a lot of room for improvement here in terms of just how much time you guys are spending.","index":497,"end_time":2149.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2144.5,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Agreed, agreed.","index":498,"end_time":2152.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2150.91,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, we, I''ve been speaking with HubSpot to do the, the SMS like marketing which would allow us to send out automated like 25k''s worth of automated messaging per month.","index":499,"end_time":2166.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2152.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And there''s, and we can do those texts in any kind of like workflow.","index":500,"end_time":2172.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2167.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So if they initially inquire, it can send out an automated text.","index":501,"end_time":2175.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2172.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If they, you know, haven''t spoken to us or we haven''t made contact with them, it could send out another text and it could be like time frame based text, all that kind of stuff.","index":502,"end_time":2185.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2175.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":503,"end_time":2185.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2185.49,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"So the only thing that they would be missing is actual context of what is happening.","index":504,"end_time":2192.05,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2186.77,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":505,"end_time":2192.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2192.369,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Like are they, are they a member?","index":506,"end_time":2194.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2192.69,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Did they used to be a member?","index":507,"end_time":2196.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2195.57,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":508,"end_time":2198.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2197.81,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So what are they?","index":509,"end_time":2200.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2198.21,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So it, I''m assuming you could feed.","index":510,"end_time":2203.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2200.45,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That into HubSpot too.","index":511,"end_time":2204.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2203.62,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"We have that information in HubSpot.","index":512,"end_time":2207.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2205.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we have.","index":513,"end_time":2208.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2208.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Whether they become an active member or they were a former member or if they''ve just been a prospect in our system.","index":514,"end_time":2215.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2208.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, again, so the direction that I''m going is kind of this AI sales assistant that actually engages in a conversation as opposed to let me just send you a text and then wait for a response and then salesperson needs to take over.","index":515,"end_time":2229.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2216.7,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So, like, that''s the direction that I''m going.","index":516,"end_time":2233.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2231.65,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"But no, that makes sense.","index":517,"end_time":2237.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2236.13,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"I mean, that sounds like a potentially great idea.","index":518,"end_time":2242.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2239.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know how you.","index":519,"end_time":2243.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2242.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What you think.","index":520,"end_time":2245.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2244.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, I agree.","index":521,"end_time":2247.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2245.17,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because on a text, they don''t know who they''re talking to.","index":522,"end_time":2249.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2247.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No, the questions are the same.","index":523,"end_time":2252.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2250.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, people ask the same questions all the time.","index":524,"end_time":2254.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2252.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And the responses are generally updated, right.","index":525,"end_time":2257.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2254.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Based on the promo of the month kind of thing.","index":526,"end_time":2259.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2257.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So, yeah, we have a chatbot that we installed on our website.","index":527,"end_time":2262.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2259.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know if you saw that.","index":528,"end_time":2263.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2262.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And Holland is that we do get people going to our.","index":529,"end_time":2268.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2263.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We get what?","index":530,"end_time":2269.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2268.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, we did the analysis, right?","index":531,"end_time":2271.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2269.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, the average user was spending almost two minutes on our website, and we were Getting maybe about 2,000.","index":532,"end_time":2276.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2271.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Over 2,000 visitors a month.","index":533,"end_time":2281.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2278.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And it was like.","index":534,"end_time":2283.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2281.97,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It was definitely like some high number.","index":535,"end_time":2285.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2283.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right?","index":536,"end_time":2285.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2285.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"High percentage of that were staying on our website.","index":537,"end_time":2287.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2285.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We don''t think we''re maximizing that inbound Traptrap website as much as we.","index":538,"end_time":2293.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2288.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We could.","index":539,"end_time":2293.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2293.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We do get those people who fill out the chat bot and talk to us, but none of that has a.","index":540,"end_time":2300.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2294.37,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''ve set up any kind of AI or automated flow.","index":541,"end_time":2304.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2300.53,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s a human.","index":542,"end_time":2304.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2304.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":543,"end_time":2305.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2305.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Mounting that ship part of it just.","index":544,"end_time":2308,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2306.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We didn''t have the capacity and time to build that up along all these other things that we''re doing.","index":545,"end_time":2315.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2308,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s another opportunity.","index":546,"end_time":2317.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2316.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think we could.","index":547,"end_time":2318.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2317.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If we had like a package solution or a playbook on how to do that, that could be.","index":548,"end_time":2323.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2318.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"A lot of.","index":549,"end_time":2324.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2323.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That could be automated too.","index":550,"end_time":2325.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2324.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Talking about the chatbot, if he.","index":551,"end_time":2327.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2325.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That is.","index":552,"end_time":2327.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2327.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, isn''t it, like, when they have questions, what happens when they start talking to it?","index":553,"end_time":2333.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2328.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is it human?","index":554,"end_time":2334.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2333.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it''s like a guided set of available responses.","index":555,"end_time":2338.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2334.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because we have a limited knowledge base for the chatbot to operate on.","index":556,"end_time":2341.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2338.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If we wanted to go an AI Chatbot, you could connect it to another knowledge base that just grows over time.","index":557,"end_time":2347.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2342.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then as it understands what the answer is to that question, it''ll just build that up.","index":558,"end_time":2352.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2347.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And whenever future inquiries come in, I think that''s what Max is alluding to.","index":559,"end_time":2356.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2352.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, Matt, you''re also talking about just a text message system, right?","index":560,"end_time":2362.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2359.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"When you text a thing, our company, you just have.","index":561,"end_time":2367.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2362.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I have another.","index":562,"end_time":2368.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2367.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s a group that.","index":563,"end_time":2369.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2368.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I know that.","index":564,"end_time":2369.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2369.43,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That does that.","index":565,"end_time":2370.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2369.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, they.","index":566,"end_time":2370.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2370.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They would just text me.","index":567,"end_time":2371.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2370.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I''m not.","index":568,"end_time":2372.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2371.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I know I''M talking to a bot, but I don''t care.","index":569,"end_time":2374.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2372.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They answer my question quickly, like right away.","index":570,"end_time":2376.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2374.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No, exactly.","index":571,"end_time":2378.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2376.71,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":572,"end_time":2378.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2378.07,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like if, if I get my question answered, I don''t care whether it''s a person that answers it or a bottom and over text, it, it bothers me less.","index":573,"end_time":2387.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2378.19,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So.","index":574,"end_time":2390.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2390.48,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, just the kind of, the AI bots that are not connected to the source of truth, to me, they''re always like, what''s the, what''s the real value?","index":575,"end_time":2407.84,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2395.76,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":576,"end_time":2408.32,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2408,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like.","index":577,"end_time":2408.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2408.32,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, context is important and I think if the idea would be to really leverage whatever context you have on all these folks you''re trying to interact with.","index":578,"end_time":2421.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2411.45,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Right.","index":579,"end_time":2421.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2421.41,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"And seems like you guys have actually done a good job of collecting a fair bit of that.","index":580,"end_time":2426.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2421.69,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Right.","index":581,"end_time":2427.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2426.73,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"So you could, I think you could do some interesting things there.","index":582,"end_time":2430.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2427.09,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Okay, so in your, I guess the.","index":583,"end_time":2439.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2433.29,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Inbound flow then.","index":584,"end_time":2441.34,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2439.5,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"I think you mentioned it translates into a credit card over the phone.","index":585,"end_time":2447.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2443.1,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"So that''s just manually typed into data track by, by whoever they''re talking to.","index":586,"end_time":2454.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2447.62,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Okay, and, and how do you guys handle scenarios where, you know, perhaps they''re not quite ready to give you a credit card but you know, they want to do a visit?","index":587,"end_time":2468.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2457.74,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"They, you know, you''re, you''re, you''re doing some sort of, some sort of, you know, guest pass situation?","index":588,"end_time":2476.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2468.76,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Like how is that handled?","index":589,"end_time":2478.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2476.92,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"So the initial call with the prospect is, the aim of the call is to set up a tour and an experience for them and to really like pitch on the value of the club.","index":590,"end_time":2490.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2479.719,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s not to just try and get the sale.","index":591,"end_time":2492.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2490.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The calls that happen where we''re getting credit card information and ACH information, those are kind of after the fact that they''ve experienced a club tour, the club, etc.","index":592,"end_time":2502.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2492.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If they express that they want to join immediately, we''re obviously getting the sale done immediately.","index":593,"end_time":2508,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2502.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But prospects tend to want to experience the club and tour the facility and you know, and like meet the personal training director, etc.","index":594,"end_time":2516.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2508.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So call one is to set up a tour and then follow up calls are to get the sale.","index":595,"end_time":2527.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2518.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You do have some people who don''t feel comfortable giving the card information over the phone.","index":596,"end_time":2533.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2528.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Those people, we tell them to either come in, in person or we just send them the link online and tell them to join online.","index":597,"end_time":2539.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2533.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And if we offered some kind of like special offer that they weren''t able to get online, we would just take care of that on the back end or I would take care of that on the back end.","index":598,"end_time":2548.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2539.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":599,"end_time":2550.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2549.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":600,"end_time":2560.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2554.77,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"No, this is awesome.","index":601,"end_time":2562.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2561.09,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"A lot to think about and definitely reinforces kind of what we''re seeing.","index":602,"end_time":2569.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2564.29,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"As.","index":603,"end_time":2571.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2571.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Far as kind of the gaps in the current tool sets.","index":604,"end_time":2574.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2571.48,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":605,"end_time":2574.64,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2574.36,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And the fact that you guys are able to kind of cobble this stuff together and I mean this kind of in the best possible way because you''re working with, you know, what''s available.","index":606,"end_time":2583.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2574.64,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"We''re probably the most technological sophisticated.","index":607,"end_time":2586.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2584,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean we have like Collins team making complex make integrations.","index":608,"end_time":2592.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2587.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think we might be a small fraction of Gems.","index":609,"end_time":2594.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2592.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know how other Equinox or how our competitors are doing this and what systems they use.","index":610,"end_time":2600.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2594.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we welcome like a better way to do this.","index":611,"end_time":2604.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2601.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think some of the HubSpot configuration work is really about processes.","index":612,"end_time":2611.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2604.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like HubSpot can do many things, but we don''t have our processes.","index":613,"end_time":2615.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2611.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Maybe we''re not clear on that.","index":614,"end_time":2618.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2615.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We don''t know what works.","index":615,"end_time":2620.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2618.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we''re trying, we''re experimenting with new processes.","index":616,"end_time":2622.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2620.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So and, and there''s a part of this that also is like continuous iteration which makes us in need of HubSpot expertise to help us design those workflows.","index":617,"end_time":2634.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2624.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The integration wasn''t.","index":618,"end_time":2636.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2635.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean it was fairly straightforward.","index":619,"end_time":2638.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2636.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I think this is, I think the tech might be there like between air call.","index":620,"end_time":2643.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2638.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know if you guys are thinking about building like an air call, but we can show you that like on site when you comment how it works.","index":621,"end_time":2649.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2643.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Um, but some of this, our questions like, well, what should happen and maybe how things is different than how another gem does it.","index":622,"end_time":2657.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2649.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Sure.","index":623,"end_time":2659.47,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2659.07,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":624,"end_time":2659.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2659.47,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":625,"end_time":2660.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2659.83,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"No.","index":626,"end_time":2660.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2660.03,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So we''re not going to build an air call, but we will use an air call.","index":627,"end_time":2662.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2660.19,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":628,"end_time":2663.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2662.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So like I have no interest in building a voiceover IP platform.","index":629,"end_time":2666.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2664.11,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Like why did that?","index":630,"end_time":2669.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2667.39,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"I don''t want to do this.","index":631,"end_time":2670.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2669.19,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah, once was good enough on that.","index":632,"end_time":2674.27,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2671.71,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"We''re good.","index":633,"end_time":2676.35,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2675.79,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"So like a mature dialer that is basically going to be, you know, that is reliable.","index":634,"end_time":2684.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2677.86,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"There''s no reason to worry about that Wheel.","index":635,"end_time":2689.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2687.22,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"I didn''t know.","index":636,"end_time":2692.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2691.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know what other CRMs could have supported us.","index":637,"end_time":2694.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2692.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"One of the big reasons we moved out of Salesforce was we couldn''t figure out how to deduplicate people.","index":638,"end_time":2699.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2694.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, and Salesforce didn''t have like a internal mailing, like mass bulk email thing.","index":639,"end_time":2707.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2700.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We had to get something else.","index":640,"end_time":2708.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2707.34,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So if we want to just keep one, anything.","index":641,"end_time":2712.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2708.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It just was hubs.","index":642,"end_time":2713.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2712.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It became like the default thing we could do.","index":643,"end_time":2716.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2713.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it might be good that you guys are thinking about like what that kind of plug and play with HubSpot could be.","index":644,"end_time":2724.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2717.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because by HubSpot you can just also use air call and you don''t have to worry about that.","index":645,"end_time":2727.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2724.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And a lot of it is just someone like Colin configurating workflows for a gym as opposed to doing anything with the integration itself.","index":646,"end_time":2735.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2727.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":647,"end_time":2738.94,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2736.46,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"It''s a great tool.","index":648,"end_time":2740.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2739.42,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":649,"end_time":2740.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2740.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But ife if I could ask you as well.","index":650,"end_time":2743.78,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2740.94,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"I think in a lot of the conversations we''ve had over the last year, a lot of the gaps were coming kind of from that ABC and Data Track side.","index":651,"end_time":2752.54,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2743.78,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Right.","index":652,"end_time":2752.78,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2752.54,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"That requires the need for a Salesforce or a HubSpot on top of that platform to be able to operate correctly.","index":653,"end_time":2759.41,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2752.78,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Do you know what some of those kind of biggest gaps are in Data Track specifically that would require somebody like Powerhouse to need a Salesforce or a HubSpot?","index":654,"end_time":2767.69,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2759.41,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Well, they don''t.","index":655,"end_time":2770.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2769.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s not a CRM, so it doesn''t, it doesn''t really do the business managing like leads coming in closing, you know, we process transactions, but a bulk of the work is pre close.","index":656,"end_time":2783.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2770.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So for a gym like ours, because we have Milan, like way you can weigh in here, like we have a team of reps, their job, a lot of their time is spend pre close.","index":657,"end_time":2794.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2784.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So a system that could handle that is not what Data Track is does.","index":658,"end_time":2800.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2794.73,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But abc, they have their own internal CRM.","index":659,"end_time":2803.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2800.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We looked at it once.","index":660,"end_time":2804.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2803.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Maybe Alex could connect you guys like to that group and you can see their demo.","index":661,"end_time":2809.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2805.61,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They had like a CRM that they were pushing for us to use at one point and it was a bit too elementary.","index":662,"end_time":2817.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2809.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like if you.","index":663,"end_time":2819.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2818.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But it''s good for you to know because if you look at it, you''ll know.","index":664,"end_time":2821.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2819.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like it''s.","index":665,"end_time":2822.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2821.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s either something that is like super elementary for maybe like a tiny gym that doesn''t need to do a lot of outbound calling, texting, not at the volume that we''re doing, or it''s, you know, or like in our case, you can see why we need all these other tech to come in.","index":666,"end_time":2837.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2822.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Did I answer your question, Wyatt?","index":667,"end_time":2840.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2838.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":668,"end_time":2841.11,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2840.71,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"No, it does.","index":669,"end_time":2841.99,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":2841.11,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"You think.","index":670,"end_time":2843.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2842.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Can we double click real quick on.","index":671,"end_time":2844.79,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2843.11,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"So what, what else happens from the standpoint of engaging?","index":672,"end_time":2849.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2844.87,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Like are you using HubSpot or any.","index":673,"end_time":2851.47,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2849.87,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Of those integrations to engage existing members, you know, to upsell, you know, either.","index":674,"end_time":2856.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2851.47,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Like, yeah, Milan, do you want to speak to.","index":675,"end_time":2858.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2856.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"For active members to upsell?","index":676,"end_time":2862.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2858.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Not right now.","index":677,"end_time":2863.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2862.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We use HubSpot once they.","index":678,"end_time":2865.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2863.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Once prospects join to get referrals.","index":679,"end_time":2869.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2865.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we.","index":680,"end_time":2870.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2870.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"To check in on their experience in case members go past due.","index":681,"end_time":2876.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2871.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We have email drip campaigns for that so that they can, you know, set their membership in good standing again.","index":682,"end_time":2882.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2876.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And that''s kind of it.","index":683,"end_time":2885.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2884.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The goal is to get personal training involved with that.","index":684,"end_time":2888.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2885.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We do do like email bulks for personal training packages and stuff, but the personal training directors haven''t quite started using HubSpot yet to be able to do that.","index":685,"end_time":2899.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2889.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The goal is to, to.","index":686,"end_time":2902.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2901.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yes, to be able to upsell with HubSpot.","index":687,"end_time":2904.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2902.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":688,"end_time":2906.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2905.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And that would mean that you would.","index":689,"end_time":2907.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2906.19,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Would have to probably channel yet more data into HubSpot, like, in terms like, like, I don''t know, you know, you''re going to see that Stan has taken two personal training classes last year.","index":690,"end_time":2918.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2907.67,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Right.","index":691,"end_time":2919.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2918.95,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"And you''re going to send Stan, you know, hey, you know, here''s your New Year''s resolution.","index":692,"end_time":2923.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2919.27,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Do we pull any of the engagement utilization stats into HubSpot now from data Track?","index":693,"end_time":2928.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2923.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":694,"end_time":2929.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2929.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I know that we.","index":695,"end_time":2930.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2929.69,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I know that we spoke about it with Call, with Michael when he was initially setting it up.","index":696,"end_time":2935.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2930.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t know if it''s currently working like with the top spenders and that kind of stuff.","index":697,"end_time":2940.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2935.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Colin, do you know.","index":698,"end_time":2941.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2940.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, I''m not.","index":699,"end_time":2947.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2946.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, this is, it isn''t a data track API.","index":700,"end_time":2954.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2950.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''ve seen it check in data transaction information.","index":701,"end_time":2957.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2954.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, yeah.","index":702,"end_time":2958.94,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2957.82,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"But you''re, I guess if you were to build a process like that, like.","index":703,"end_time":2966.34,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2962.38,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"The, I guess the business logic associated with like what you offer and to whom you would today be building that in HubSpot, I presume.","index":704,"end_time":2975.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2966.34,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"We would connect it to.","index":705,"end_time":2983.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2981.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We would find.","index":706,"end_time":2984.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2983.77,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":707,"end_time":2987.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2985.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If you were to design a process.","index":708,"end_time":2989.29,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2987.61,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"That would, you know, try to optimize either, you know, selling packages or, you know, in any kind of, let''s call it existing member outreach today, this would be, you know, build, like, I guess.","index":709,"end_time":3005.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2989.37,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"You kind of have two moves given.","index":710,"end_time":3006.66,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3005.14,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"I guess, the limitations of Data Track, from what I understand, it would either be to use it, you know, to.","index":711,"end_time":3013.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3006.82,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Build that whole thing in HubSpot or.","index":712,"end_time":3015.22,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3013.22,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"To, you know, use some, you know, outside tools.","index":713,"end_time":3020.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3015.3,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Right.","index":714,"end_time":3020.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3020.5,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Let''s just say you know, anything from Excel.","index":715,"end_time":3022.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3020.74,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Right.","index":716,"end_time":3023.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3022.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"To something else in between, and then simply populate the outcome of that into.","index":717,"end_time":3028.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3023.54,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Into HubSpot in terms of the actual campaigns you want to run.","index":718,"end_time":3031.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3028.97,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Correct?","index":719,"end_time":3032.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3032.41,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":720,"end_time":3033.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3033.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":721,"end_time":3034.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3033.61,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And so right now, for example, the personal training department pulls lists for like new members or potential clients from Data Track and then they use like just the land lights to call these members.","index":722,"end_time":3049.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3034.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it''s like very rudimentary.","index":723,"end_time":3052.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3050.33,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But yeah, I think in future, I think it would be something that would be built out in HubSpot.","index":724,"end_time":3058.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3053.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so then to follow up on Stan''s question, then ife from the business perspective, once you guys are doing those kinds of things.","index":725,"end_time":3065.16,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3059.16,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"What''s your current method of tracking the results from those efforts?","index":726,"end_time":3069.72,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3065.16,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Where would you be going to find that information?","index":727,"end_time":3071.8,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3069.8,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Maybe Milan can answer this question.","index":728,"end_time":3078.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3077.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You might have to clarify a bit more like finding out if they''ve.","index":729,"end_time":3081.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3078.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Sure.","index":730,"end_time":3082.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3081.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Saying I want to look last month and see how many people signed up for personal training packages.","index":731,"end_time":3085.96,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3082.12,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Data track.","index":732,"end_time":3087.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3087.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, me too.","index":733,"end_time":3090.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3088.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But I want to see how many calls my, my personal trainers have done to get new launch assessments set up.","index":734,"end_time":3098.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3091.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You can''t do that right now with the way they''re doing it.","index":735,"end_time":3101.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3098.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That would have to be done on HubSpot.","index":736,"end_time":3102.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3101.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":737,"end_time":3104.2,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3103.8,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"And then you''re gonna have to piece it together like we talked about.","index":738,"end_time":3106.28,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3104.2,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Like from my perspective, if I was in sales leadership.","index":739,"end_time":3109.12,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3106.28,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Right.","index":740,"end_time":3109.32,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3109.12,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Maybe I want to see how many total calls went out and how many total memberships we signed.","index":741,"end_time":3112.68,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3109.32,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Just that basic metric relationship.","index":742,"end_time":3115.22,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3113.38,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"You''d have to go to multiple sources and then put that in Excel.","index":743,"end_time":3118.86,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3115.54,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Right?","index":744,"end_time":3119.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3118.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I think there''s a, like if you came, if you said what do we do we need that.","index":745,"end_time":3125.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3119.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that like a hair on fire or thing?","index":746,"end_time":3128.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3125.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like I think we would want to unpack.","index":747,"end_time":3131.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3128.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like what are the, how do we measure roi?","index":748,"end_time":3134.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3131.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How do, how do what bandwidth and capacity.","index":749,"end_time":3137.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3134.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have to measure roi.","index":750,"end_time":3138.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3137.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And it might be that like for our, for us.","index":751,"end_time":3140.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3138.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, you''ve asked for that in some ways too, in a very basic kind of way.","index":752,"end_time":3145.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3141.19,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we''re also like a high volume big box gym.","index":753,"end_time":3148.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3145.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we''re, we''re not going to be able to like optimize perfectly for, do this thing.","index":754,"end_time":3154.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3148.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I, I guess differently for this particular lead.","index":755,"end_time":3159.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3155.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like to the extent that we know some reps are not as effective, that might help us do deliver better training to that rep.","index":756,"end_time":3167.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3160.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But there''s only so much I think analysis too that we can wrap our head around.","index":757,"end_time":3171.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3168,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But some of that right now doesn''t really exist.","index":758,"end_time":3175.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3173.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s hard to pull.","index":759,"end_time":3175.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3175.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I would wonder if for like Jim''s much smaller, do they, would they even care about like what is the effort that went into trying to convert this individual lead and will we even have time to kind of debrief that?","index":760,"end_time":3190.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3175.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we at a high, at the highest level, like anything that could help us know if we could be more deliver like better support, I guess.","index":761,"end_time":3200.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3191.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, like right now it''s all analog.","index":762,"end_time":3202.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3200.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like you''re just anecdotally like sitting at the table like listening to people and you''re talking to the reps. You''re not really using any data, are you right now to help you determine who needs more help and support?","index":763,"end_time":3214.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3202.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, I mean we have the Voice recordings and things like that.","index":764,"end_time":3219.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3217.11,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I, I go through.","index":765,"end_time":3220.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3219.91,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, you watch that.","index":766,"end_time":3223.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3221.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, exactly.","index":767,"end_time":3224.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3223.11,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":768,"end_time":3225.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3224.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So like if you zoom out, just.","index":769,"end_time":3228.87,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3227.31,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Like a basic question, like, you know.","index":770,"end_time":3230.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3228.87,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"I want to gauge the efficacy of.","index":771,"end_time":3233.55,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3230.75,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"A particular, you know, personal training, you know, package sales campaign on the number of personal, you know, on personal training revenue.","index":772,"end_time":3242.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3233.55,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Right.","index":773,"end_time":3242.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3242.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This month.","index":774,"end_time":3243.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3242.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":775,"end_time":3243.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3243.07,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"For example.","index":776,"end_time":3244.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3243.43,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Right.","index":777,"end_time":3244.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3244.51,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Like a very basic, like, you know, I want to see which, you know, which promotions work better.","index":778,"end_time":3250.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3244.87,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Right.","index":779,"end_time":3251.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3251.14,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, do you guys do that today or have the capability to do that today?","index":780,"end_time":3255.86,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3251.62,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"And, and would that be valuable if you don''t?","index":781,"end_time":3259.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3257.38,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"It would be valuable.","index":782,"end_time":3261.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3260.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I, I don''t run the personal training department, so I, I can''t speak for them, but I don''t think they''re measuring those kind of things.","index":783,"end_time":3271.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3262.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, well, so it''s that.","index":784,"end_time":3275.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3274.35,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"But also, let''s say you have three reps right now, right.","index":785,"end_time":3280.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3275.87,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"On aggregate, let''s say kind of, you''re getting kind of the leads and your membership stats, they''re doing good.","index":786,"end_time":3290.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3280.91,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"But out of those three, only two are doing a good job.","index":787,"end_time":3294.99,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3290.99,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And the third one is kind of like hiding in the midst.","index":788,"end_time":3297.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3294.99,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Like, would you know that your third sales rep is actually underperforming and I need to manage amount replacements.","index":789,"end_time":3303.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3297.15,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yes.","index":790,"end_time":3304.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3304.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Through number of sales, through closing percentages in the different lead buckets, that kind of stuff.","index":791,"end_time":3310.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3305.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yes.","index":792,"end_time":3310.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3310.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So you will know that through HubSpot.","index":793,"end_time":3313.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3310.6,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"HubSpot, correct.","index":794,"end_time":3315.76,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3313.84,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":795,"end_time":3319.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3319.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s no way, is there a way to Milan to know what, what''s our conversion on like Facebook?","index":796,"end_time":3329.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3319.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because that''s coming from HubSpot.","index":797,"end_time":3332.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3330.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Now, Colin, do you know to see like in a given month how many leads of the November, October cohort converted to paid members?","index":798,"end_time":3345.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3332.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":799,"end_time":3346.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3345.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean we could run a report that basically just says if this was their conversion, are they a member?","index":800,"end_time":3350.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3346.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we just get that number.","index":801,"end_time":3351.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3350.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"HubSpot has all that information.","index":802,"end_time":3354.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3353.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re not, we may not be looking at that today.","index":803,"end_time":3359.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3356.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No.","index":804,"end_time":3360.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3360.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I mean, if we can build it.","index":805,"end_time":3362.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3360.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":806,"end_time":3363.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3363.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that, that might be on us.","index":807,"end_time":3365.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3363.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we haven''t gotten there.","index":808,"end_time":3366.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3365.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What we have, the extent we''ve looked at it is cost per lead and how many leads we get based on the budget we''ve spent.","index":809,"end_time":3372.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3366.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But then there''s another drop off from getting the lead to them making a sale that we, that''s a kind of a, we don''t know what that is yet.","index":810,"end_time":3384.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3372.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":811,"end_time":3388.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3388.08,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Okay, so I may have missed it, but now.","index":812,"end_time":3395.52,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3390.72,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So you guys don''t really have like an upsell motion per se.","index":813,"end_time":3400.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3395.52,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":814,"end_time":3400.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3400.24,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So you''re more focused on just getting new members, right?","index":815,"end_time":3403.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3400.56,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yes, yes.","index":816,"end_time":3407.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3406.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The only Upsell that we really have at both the gyms is going to be setting up like a complimentary launch assessment which will be meet a meeting basically with the personal training director and then that personal training director will try and pitch personal training.","index":817,"end_time":3422.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3408.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And that''s the only upsell.","index":818,"end_time":3423.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3422.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Keeping people and probably keeping them paying their dues is also is pressing.","index":819,"end_time":3430.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3424.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We may soon have it because we are.","index":820,"end_time":3432.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3430.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We just hired a new director of like group fitness person who''s gonna build up a group fitness program.","index":821,"end_time":3438.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3432.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean there is the PT side.","index":822,"end_time":3440.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3439.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think PT just right now organizationally they''re like a.","index":823,"end_time":3444.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3440.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s.","index":824,"end_time":3445.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3445.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re still learning how to like maximize.","index":825,"end_time":3450.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3445.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"PD''s doing great, but they''re also kind of just.","index":826,"end_time":3452.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3450.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They''re doing great in asylum maybe there''s more potential there.","index":827,"end_time":3455.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3452.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we have a term, you know, we still have people leaving the gym like and we, we don''t have a right.","index":828,"end_time":3465.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3456.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean correct me, I''m wrong.","index":829,"end_time":3466.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3465.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we don''t have a great, great answer to how to deal with that, how to communicate to them.","index":830,"end_time":3472.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3466.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What''s the playbook on that.","index":831,"end_time":3473.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3472.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We just, we''re just like hopefully one net new.","index":832,"end_time":3478.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3474.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''ll net more members coming in than people leaving.","index":833,"end_time":3481.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3478.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":834,"end_time":3482.94,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3482.66,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Ife do you.","index":835,"end_time":3483.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3482.94,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Do you have a good way now to look at kind of who the Personas are that are churning versus not and be able to say, hey, when you know, people check in X times a month, they''re less likely if they''re involved in a class or pt they''re less likely to churn.","index":836,"end_time":3494.66,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3483.86,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Do we know what any of those characteristics are?","index":837,"end_time":3497.46,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3495.06,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"I want to say like, honestly, like no part there''s a.","index":838,"end_time":3507.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3502.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What''s contributing to that is Data track is not accurate.","index":839,"end_time":3511.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3507.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s different reports that show different numbers and Alex and I can''t get our mind around why that is the case.","index":840,"end_time":3518.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3511.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And even data track can''t answer the question.","index":841,"end_time":3521.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3518.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan just brought up some piece that shows up in one report and data tracks.","index":842,"end_time":3524.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3521.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know who these people are.","index":843,"end_time":3525.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3524.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They don''t exist in the other thing.","index":844,"end_time":3527.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3525.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We don''t know the answer.","index":845,"end_time":3528.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3527.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Basic things like that that makes it hard to even look at it.","index":846,"end_time":3534.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3528.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But there is some things that we can run to kind of look at like the reasons and like we''ve done that before.","index":847,"end_time":3539.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3534.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I, I don''t think it''s as.","index":848,"end_time":3542.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3539.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We could do a much better job of it by I think having more documentation on why people leave.","index":849,"end_time":3554.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3544.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not like hoping that they''ll fill out a survey or just like enter a drop down and that''s the only information that we need.","index":850,"end_time":3562.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3554.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s so much more to it and we haven''t done any concerted efforts so far of really learning and talking.","index":851,"end_time":3568.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3562.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Talking to users or talking.","index":852,"end_time":3570.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3568.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":853,"end_time":3572.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3571.88,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So this will be hard for you to get to.","index":854,"end_time":3574.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3572.24,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Why the best thing that you can do is you can create these customer cohorts.","index":855,"end_time":3581.32,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3574.8,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":856,"end_time":3581.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3581.56,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"That basically like when people leave, this is their behavior.","index":857,"end_time":3586.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3581.92,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Right.","index":858,"end_time":3587.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3587.53,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So as in like I haven''t checked in or I haven''t visited the gym in the last six months.","index":859,"end_time":3593.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3587.77,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So I''m probably in the churn bucket.","index":860,"end_time":3595.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3593.53,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"But when my contract expires.","index":861,"end_time":3598.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3596.41,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So like things like that.","index":862,"end_time":3599.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3598.13,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So it''s, it''s.","index":863,"end_time":3600.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3599.93,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Is that like a different.","index":864,"end_time":3602.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3601.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like in my past, like we have software for that.","index":865,"end_time":3605.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3602.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that a HubSpot thing?","index":866,"end_time":3607.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3605.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No.","index":867,"end_time":3607.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3607.37,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Or in my experience, like it''s.","index":868,"end_time":3609.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3607.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"There''s other tools that help us do that kind of thing.","index":869,"end_time":3612.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3609.45,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":870,"end_time":3612.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3612.01,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t think those tools exist in the health and fitness.","index":871,"end_time":3616.58,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3613.14,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":872,"end_time":3617.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3617.46,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So this is like what you would call in SaaS when you''re looking at the impact net retention.","index":873,"end_time":3627.06,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3617.9,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"You can look at these customer cohorts and basically at the customer''s health scores.","index":874,"end_time":3635.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3628.02,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So I don''t love that analogy in health clubs, but is a customer that exhibits certain behavior, are they more likely to stay, are they more likely to leave?","index":875,"end_time":3649.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3637.62,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And then you have a lot of historical data.","index":876,"end_time":3652.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3650.44,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So all of this is trapped inside of data Track.","index":877,"end_time":3655.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3652.96,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"This is probably my mind goes to like this is detective work.","index":878,"end_time":3660.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3655.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we would run reports in data track, different reports, believe that it''s accurate and then do some fancy Excel magic to try to connect like link different members activity with when they turned kind of thing.","index":879,"end_time":3674.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3660.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, for now like that''s to do that.","index":880,"end_time":3678.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3676.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We would probably do something like that.","index":881,"end_time":3680.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3678.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"This is an area of opportunity for us for sure.","index":882,"end_time":3683.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3680.92,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Agreed.","index":883,"end_time":3684.759,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3684.32,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"And I think for me internally I''d just like to know whether some of that you can take action on.","index":884,"end_time":3689,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3684.759,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Of course.","index":885,"end_time":3689.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3689,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Other things I''d just love to know internally, you know.","index":886,"end_time":3693.48,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3690,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"So how many, how many members do I have that are my group A, B and C and D group where group A, you know, is checking in X amount of times per month and maybe has a class they''re signed up for and then understand kind of how to move people between those buckets and see if it impacts churn.","index":887,"end_time":3707.23,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":3693.48,"speaker_name":"Wyatt Callow"},{"text":"Hey Colin, there''s a.","index":888,"end_time":3709.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3708.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is this meeting going to close out here in two minutes?","index":889,"end_time":3711.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3709.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I''m hosting a.","index":890,"end_time":3714.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3712.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Another call that starts.","index":891,"end_time":3716.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3714.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Can you send the recording to us for this one and then.","index":892,"end_time":3719.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3717.07,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, guys, yeah, we''ll, we''ll pick though.","index":893,"end_time":3722.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3720.75,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"We''ll pick this up.","index":894,"end_time":3722.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3722.23,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"There''s there''s a lot to unfold here and to continue the conversation.","index":895,"end_time":3725.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3722.87,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And so, guys, thank you very much.","index":896,"end_time":3727.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3725.71,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"It''s been super informative.","index":897,"end_time":3730.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3728.51,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Super informative.","index":898,"end_time":3731.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3730.75,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"And Ife and Nilan, we''re looking forward to seeing you guys next week.","index":899,"end_time":3735.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3731.87,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"So it''ll be a lot of fun.","index":900,"end_time":3736.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3735.11,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Likewise.","index":901,"end_time":3738.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3737.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":902,"end_time":3739.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3738.99,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"All right.","index":903,"end_time":3739.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3739.43,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Thank you, everybody.","index":904,"end_time":3740.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3739.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks, guys.","index":905,"end_time":3740.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3740.35,"speaker_name":"Stan Reznik"},{"text":"Bye.","index":906,"end_time":3741.23,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3740.87,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":907,"end_time":3742.23,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3741.79,"speaker_name":"Max Longin"}],"dateString":"2025-11-07T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86203110224?pwd=3XPsDxD6j7Dde4nHk4bPeJruRpCvww.1","participants":["yefei@yhatinvest.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com,wyattcallow@gmail.com,max@motioniq.us,stan@motioniq.us","yefei@yhatinvest.com","milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com","nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","wyattcallow@gmail.com","max@motioniq.us","stan@motioniq.us"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01K99ZJ22YJJTRB4EYM1PP1JAY","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.87,"bullets":["Outlined full HubSpot-to-DataTrack user journey; highlighted manual steps and improvement areas.","Colin confirmed Meta leads integrate directly with HubSpot via mapped contact submission.","Stan proposed AI-assisted workflows to reduce rep manual entry and improve lead response time.","Milan detailed reps make ~2,000 calls and ~3,000 texts per week with mostly manual logging.","Yefei confirmed integration time largely spent on sales process setup, not API connections."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Most of the time is working with Milan on like sales process and workflow changes.","speaker":"Colin Costigan"},{"quote":"So we welcome like a better way to do this.","speaker":"Yefei Jin"},{"quote":"Creating an easy process around this would be valuable.","speaker":"Stan Reznik"}],"topics":["crm","workflow","integration","automation","salesops","retention"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-11-11T23:29:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **CRM and Lead Management Integration**\n\nThe team confirmed that **HubSpot** serves as the primary CRM with direct integration from **Meta ads** and website forms, streamlining lead capture and routing for sales follow-up (08:36).\n\n- Leads enter HubSpot either via Meta ads or website forms replaced with HubSpot forms, ensuring immediate capture and triggering drip campaigns (11:16).\n- The transition from HubSpot to **Data Track** is manual, requiring duplicate data entry and creating inefficiencies; this was highlighted as the biggest pain point by **Colin Costigan** and **Milan Wagner** (15:37).\n- The integration between HubSpot and Data Track relies on periodic polling via APIs every five minutes, incurring a monthly operational cost around **$300-$500** due to high volume usage (19:04).\n- HubSpot’s configuration, including custom objects and workflows, was tailored to fit the gym''s sales process, with **Colin** emphasizing that most time went into customizing workflows rather than building the integration itself (21:30).\n\n## **Sales and Communication Workflows**\n\nCurrent sales outreach is heavily manual, involving high-volume calling and texting supported by HubSpot and Air Call integrations, with room for automation improvement (31:17).\n\n- Sales reps make between **60 to 100 calls daily** each, totaling over **2,000 calls weekly**, and send up to **15,000 texts weekly**, all manually initiated via HubSpot-linked Air Call (32:05).\n- Lead outreach follows a cadence of **five to six contact attempts on day one**, combining calls, texts, and emails, with ongoing monthly follow-ups based on lead age and engagement (33:06).\n- Air Call manages inbound calls via a call queue system with fallback to a designated rep after missed calls, but lacks virtual receptionist or AI answering features currently (29:09).\n- The team is exploring HubSpot’s SMS marketing workflows to automate up to **25,000 messages per month**, which could reduce manual texting burden and improve lead engagement (35:50).\n\n## **Process Gaps and Limitations in Data Track**\n\nData Track lacks CRM capabilities and fails to support lead management, contract signing, and member engagement processes, necessitating additional platforms like HubSpot (46:09).\n\n- Data Track does not create lead accounts upon online waiver or phone signup, requiring reps to manually input member info and process payments, increasing administrative load (15:46).\n- Contract signing is manual or in-person only, with no electronic signature support, causing missed agreements and compliance risks as some liability forms are not captured timely (13:07).\n- Data Track’s reporting on member activity and churn is inconsistent and unreliable, complicating efforts to analyze retention, engagement, and sales effectiveness (58:22).\n- The personal training upsell and member engagement functions are rudimentary, relying on manual list pulls from Data Track and offline calling, with no current automation or campaign tracking (50:59).\n\n## **Analytics, Reporting, and Member Retention**\n\nThe group identified a pressing need for better visibility into sales performance, lead conversion, and member churn to drive smarter decision-making (53:47).\n\n- HubSpot can generate reports to track lead-to-member conversion rates by cohort, but this capability has not been fully leveraged by the team yet (55:46).\n- Sales leadership currently relies on manual tracking of individual rep performance through closing percentages and call volumes, but lacks integrated dashboards combining calls, texts, and sales results (54:34).\n- Understanding member churn drivers and personas is hindered by inconsistent Data Track data, limiting the ability to target retention efforts effectively (58:22).\n- The team expressed interest in cohort analysis and customer health scoring concepts from SaaS, aiming to segment members by behavior to predict and reduce churn, but lacks tools to implement this yet (01:00:55).\n\n## **Future Automation and AI Opportunities**\n\nThere is strong interest in exploring AI-driven communication and automation to improve customer engagement and reduce manual workload (36:25).\n\n- **Max Longin** proposed developing an AI sales assistant capable of conversational texting to answer common questions and engage leads before handing off to sales reps (36:40).\n- The current website chatbot handles limited guided responses from a fixed knowledge base; expanding this with AI and connecting it to dynamic data would enhance user experience (38:47).\n- Automation of lead engagement through HubSpot workflows, including SMS drip campaigns, is under consideration to increase touchpoints and improve conversion rates (35:50).\n- The team acknowledged that while AI bots may be recognized as non-human, quick and contextually accurate answers over text are highly valued by customers (39:19).\n\n## **Implementation and Next Steps**\n\nThe group agreed to continue refining workflows and integrations with HubSpot expertise, focusing on process clarity, automation, and better data utilization (43:04).\n\n- **Colin Costigan** and team will work on exporting and templating HubSpot configurations to enable easier deployment across new instances or platforms, aiming for rapid replication (25:29).\n- Discussions will continue on improving the manual signup process and contract capture, with potential solutions to be presented in the coming days by **Stan Reznik’s** team (14:16).\n- The team emphasized the need for ongoing iteration and expertise in sales workflow design to fully leverage HubSpot’s capabilities beyond just integration (44:19).\n- The call concluded with plans to resume the conversation next week, focusing on gaps identified and potential tech-enabled improvements to sales and member management processes (01:02:02).","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot","Data Track","CRM Integration","Aircall","Lead Management","Sales Workflows"],"overview":"- **CRM Integration:** HubSpot integrates with Meta ads and website forms for seamless lead capture and automatic drip campaigns.\n\n- **Manual Processes:** Lead transfer to Data Track is manual, causing inefficiencies and requiring duplicate data entry.\n\n- **Calling & Texting Volume:** Sales reps make 60-100 calls daily, totaling over 2,000 calls weekly, with manual texting efforts as well.\n\n- **Data Track Limitations:** Lacks CRM functions, leading to manual lead account creation and contract signing, increasing administrative workload.\n\n- **Analytics Needs:** Improved visibility into sales performance and churn metrics is essential to enhance decision-making and retention strategies.\n\n- **AI Opportunities:** Exploring AI-driven communication tools to streamline engagement and reduce manual workloads is a priority moving forward.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nProvide meeting recording to all participants (01:01:45)\nAssist with exporting HubSpot property configurations and workflows for duplication or integration (16:40)\n\n**Milan Wagner**\nSupport modification and presentation of HubSpot sales process workflows (21:00)\nManage and track outbound call/text campaign metrics and sales rep activity (50:25)\n\n**Yefei Jin**\nCoordinate feedback and review proposed signup workflow improvements from Stan Reznik and others (14:45)\n\n**Stan Reznik**\nDraft and share enhanced manual phone signup workflow proposals with Powerhouse team (14:40)\nContinue conversation on optimizing sales and retention workflows with Powerhouse (01:02:00)\n\n**Max Longin**\nAnalyze potential for AI-driven texting assistant integrated with HubSpot and Data Track (36:00)\nExplore development of integration app for replication of HubSpot sales process in other gyms/platforms (22:30)\n\n**Wyatt Callow**\nInvestigate sales call and member engagement data collection improvements (30:05)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"1ee09514-31cd-40ef-9afc-e9654969aecd","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
